Hey hello, this is Tapas, have been a tour guide since 2009 for Sreemangal and around Bangladesh. With a passion for tourism, I am here to make your stay unforgettable. Having traveled to multiple countries, I know how to offer top-notch guest services. I'll gladly recommend the best tourist hotspots in Sreemangal and around. So come on over and let me show you the time of your life!

I’m a British Bangladeshi currently working as an IT consultant in the UK. I love traveling and hosting guests.

The Mayfair, a modern holiday home in Sreemangal, Bangladesh, has been designed by me and my wife so we can retreat from our busy life in England to have some quality time near to nature. 

Whilst we are not there, you are welcome to stay at The Mayfair, unwind, relax, enjoy the tourist attractions and take some great memories away.
